Description

Brand : Tamachan Shop

Package Dimensions : 10 10 10 cm; 1 Kg

Is Discontinued By Manufacturer : No

Form : Powder

Appropriate Age Range : Adult

Manufacturer : Kyunan Service Ltd.

Country of Origin : Japan

Additives : Collagen

[Konayuki Collagen 100,000mg 10 bags set] The first squeezed raw material using domestic pigskin is further purified with our own new technology and made into peptides. Tasteless and odorless, we have cut out all the sugars and fats inherent in pork, and have realized the highest quality low-molecular-weight collagen that is additive-free, color-free, and fragrance-free. [Nutritional Ingredients] Assuming a daily intake of 10g (per 10000mg), the average daily calorie intake for women is compared to the national average of 1800-2200kcal Calories: 37.8kcal Protein: 9.44g Fat: 0.01g Carbohydrate: 0g Salt Equivalent amount: 0.04g Even those on a diet can use it with confidence. Ingredients/Ingredients Pig Skin Collagen Peptide (Contains gelatin) *Please refer to the ingredients and refrain from using if you have allergies. Also, if it does not suit your physical condition or constitution, do not use it. How to use Dissolve 3-10g in a drink or dish and enjoy.
